Description: 'Globus' is a cloud-based file transfer service,
    available at <https://www.globus.org/>. This package provides an
    'R' client with the ability to discover and navigate file
    collections, and to transfer files and directories between
    collections. Use of the package is illustrated with data from the
    'HuBMAP' <https://portal.hubmapconsortium.org/> data portal and
    'HuBMAPR' package.
